import { Button } from "bootstrap";
import React from "react";
import { Col, Container, Row } from "react-bootstrap";
import "./Style.css";

const Main = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Row>
        <Col className="mt-5 ml-5 mb-5">
        <Container className="container1">
          {/* Name  */}
          <Row className="">
            <input type="text" placeholder="First Name" className="email" />
          </Row>
          <Row className="mt-2">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Last name" className="email" />
          </Row>
          <Row className="mt-2">
            <input type="email" placeholder="Email" className="email" />
          </Row>
          <Row className="mt-2">
            <input type="number" placeholder="Phone " className="email" />
          </Row>
          <Row className="mt-2">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Profession" className="email" />
          </Row>
          <Row className="mt-2">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Street" className="email" />
          </Row>
          <Row className="mt-2">
            <input type="text" placeholder="City" className="email" />
          </Row>
          <Row className="mt-2 ">
            <input type="text" placeholder="State" className="email" />
          </Row>
          <Row className="mt-2">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Country" className="email" />
          </Row>
          <Row className="mt-2 mb-1">
            <input type="number" placeholder="Pin Code" className="email" />
          </Row>
          <Row> <button>Add</button></Row>
          </Container>
        </Col>

        <Col></Col>
        <Col></Col>
      </Row>
    </>
  );
};

export default Main;
